info.name: Snowflake Password Policy API
info.description:
The Snowflake Password Policy API is a REST API that you can use to access, update, and perform certain actions on Password Policy resource in a Snowflake database.

Contact Support:
 Name: Snowflake, Inc.
 Email: support@snowflake.com
